        <div class="faq__answer" id="kitchen-sink-d3-state-pillar-faq-a7" data-open="false">
          <p>Book a free 30-minute discovery call. We review your New York operational context (NYC vs. upstate, industry, multi-state exposure), recommend the right engagement structure, and deliver a written fixed-fee scope within 3 business days. Same-day diagnostic for emergencies.</p>
