          <p>New York applies sales tax to a broader range of services than most states &mdash; including certain information services, interior design, cleaning, parking, and telecommunications. The combined rate in New York City is 8.875% (4% state + 4.5% NYC + 0.375% MTA surcharge). QuickBooks must be configured with the correct tax codes per service type and customer location. Misconfiguration &mdash; particularly for agencies, media firms, and professional-services businesses with mixed taxable and exempt revenue &mdash; is among the most common NY QuickBooks issues we correct.</p>
